                                            <h2>How it Can Help You Now</h2>
                                            <p>Once Einstein Analytics has access to your data, past and present, it will start creating visualizations to help you better understand where your company is at right now. It will suggest solutions for inventory discrepancies, room rate disparities, team performance, customer satisfaction, and anything else that it notices needing attention. Don’t worry about having to manually input data or reports again; with Einstein Analytics, it will automatically transfer data from CSV files or any other external data records.</p>
                                            <div class="costumer-page__view-list_section">
                                               <p>Einstein AI will generate reports as often as you want, providing you with unbiased suggestions and facts from each day’s information haul. Your marketing team, customer service team, and sales team can make great use of the information that this program organizes. You can even customize your own personal dashboard to present you with the data that you specifically need.</p>
                                            </div>
